title: Deezer Downloader v1.4.9 Apk - Download Music in High Quality
description:
Download Music from Deezer in full 320Kbps Quality and in Flac (For Free) 

This app allows you to search for and download any songs at the highest quality (320kbps). The files are downloaded with high quality album artwork and the track name, number, artist name, album name, release year (and other information) are all downloaded with the track into a single MP3 file.
